name: Crimson-down-Mix
description:
This is my first mix, in which I tried to make colorful backgrounds.

Please, write all pros and cons of the checkpoint, your comments and reviews allow me to remakeit (cause I have no possibility to check it properly) and to make my future projects better.

I recommend use kl-hf or orange-mix VAE for it.

Also you can support me on ko-fi and Patreon.
